title: Dead Trigger 2 Tegra 4 Graphics For All Device APK + SD Data
description:
1. First force stop Dead Trigger 2 App in Application settings
2. Just copy the attached file to /data/data/com.madfingergames.deadtrigger2/shared_prefs/
3. Done! Enjoy!

It will spoof your device so that the game thinks it's a Tegra 4 powered one and unleash the ultra highest effects which is only available for Tegra 4.

The default resoulution is set to 1920*1080. You can change it if your device does not support that kind of resolution. This is the highest settings so running it on lower end device might derive some lag. I did not made any custom apk, i just provided the setting so that you can Customize on your own (and learn some coding
;). 

Edit this 2 lines to change the screen res according your device.

<int name="Screenmanager Resolution Width" value="1920"/>
....
<int name="Screenmanager Resolution Height" value="1080"/>

All the Best!
